README.md
# Construction HRMS QA Assignment

This repository contains my submission for the DeepThought QA Engineer assignment.

## Objectives

* Build a quality strategy for a construction HRMS.
* Design acceptance criteria.
* Perform exploratory and negative testing.
* Build regression and automated test suites.
* Implement CI/CD quality gates.

## Repository Structure

```
test-strategy.md
quality-reflection.md
specs/
bug-reports/
tests/
test-data/
.github/
```

The primary goal of this project is to protect the payroll pipeline and reduce production failures that directly affect construction workers.
